Class BodyParts

java.lang.Object
application.BodyParts
Direct Known Subclasses:
Eyes, Glasses, Goatee, Hair, Head, Mole, Mouth, Mustache, Nose, Torso
public class BodyParts extends Object
Abstract class that all of the part parts will inherit from. It includes basic items and functions that are needed to set and get the accessories
Author:
Joy Janney
